<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-care-of">take care of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-care-for-look-after">1.<strong>照顾；照料 (care for / look after)； 处理：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It has been my duty to help my mom take care of my little brothers and sisters. 
帮妈妈照顾弟弟妹妹已经成了我的职责。</p><footer>2014 广东</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A man too busy to take care of his health is like a mechanic too busy to take care of his tools.
人忙得无暇爱惜自己的身体就如机械师忙得无暇爱护自己的工具一样。</p><footer>人教⑤ – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Will you take care of buying fruit for tonight's party?
你负责为今晚的聚会买水果好吗？</p></div></div>